<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ش ظ ي:</span> <span class="c2">(الشَّظِيَّةُ)</span> الْفِلْقَةُ مِنَ الْعَصَا وَنَحْوِهَا وَالْجَمْعُ <span class="c2">(الشَّظَايَا)</span> .<span class="c5"> يُقَالُ:</span> <span class="c2">(تَشَظَّى)</span> الشَّيْءُ إِذَا تَطَايَرَ شَظَايَاهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>